description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Dynamic Warm-Up' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Groove Session vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Warm up your body with Peter through some mobility and bodyweight exercises to prepare you for any type of workout. ...
